WEBVTT

00:00:58.830 --> 00:01:02.283
that made it possible for them
to use mobile computing,

00:01:02.307 --> 00:01:05.591
regardless of who they were
and their abilities.

00:01:06.814 --> 00:01:08.391
Now for most of us,

00:01:08.415 --> 00:01:11.196
the impact of this technology

00:01:11.220 --> 00:01:13.503
is to make things
a little bit easier to use.

00:01:13.916 --> 00:01:16.095
But for my friend Daniel,

00:01:17.352 --> 00:01:20.523
the impact of the AI
in these systems is a life changer.

00:01:21.217 --> 00:01:26.050
You see, Daniel is a really social guy,

00:01:26.074 --> 00:01:27.833
and he's blind and quadriplegic,

00:01:28.614 --> 00:01:32.473
which makes it hard to use those devices
that we all take for granted.